Trade/Device Name(s): Healgen MDMA (Ecstasy) Test (Strip, Cassette, Cup, Dip Card)
Healgen Phencyclidine Test (Strip, Cassette, Cup, Dip Card)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Healgen MDMA (Ecstasy) and Phencyclidine Tests for qualitative detection of drugs of abuse in urine using immunochromatographic lateral flow assays
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection of methylenedioxymethamphetamine (MDMA, Ecstasy) at 500 ng/mL and phencyclidine at 25 ng/mL in human urine for prescription and over-the-counter in vitro diagnostic use
